<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.6">
<l>kallāvaim pulaṉka ḷavaikaṇṭavā ṟuceyyakillēṉ.</l>
<l>mallāmal lamaruḷ mallarmāḷamal laṭartta</l>
<l>mallāmal lalamcīr matiḷnīrilaṅ kaiyaḻitta</l>
<l>villāniṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Strong [lord], I cannot act the capricious way of [my] ignorant five senses.</l>
<l>Strong [lord] who wrestled so that the wrestlers died in a wrestling match,</l>
<l>You with the bow who destroyed Laṅkā [girded by] water</l>
<l rend="indent">and a fine, beautiful, strong wall,</l>
<l>I take refuge in you, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
